&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you looking for a new challenge?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We have recently under gone a huge rebuild housing the Emergency Department, AECU (Ambulatory Emergency Care Unit) AAU (Acute Assessment Unit) &amp; SSU (Surgical Short Stay Unit). If you are looking for a new career in a state of the art facility and fast moving environment then this may be the challenge you are looking for.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt; We have a team of ward clerks that rotate between all three units and are looking for someone who is adaptable, friendly and hard working. We are looking for someone to work in a variety of shifts within a seven day period. This role will include working bank holidays.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Shifts - 07:00-15:00 or 14:00-22:00&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Doreen Bader (Senior Team Leader) on 07774016579&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
